    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Thanks for the link. \r\n\r\nThe discussion I see there seems like an argument for completely deprecating describe. \r\n\r\nI can respect that, but if you are going to keep it in the project, why not expand it to include common aggregations like sum, which is prominently featured in the examples for the agg expansion? Having both seems like a road to confusion for users."
